{"sha": "b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0MTM2NTMxMDA6YjUxZGUxM2Q4MTkyMGY5MmViZTA2N2I5Yzc2ZTlkMjE5NTY4NTA5OQ==", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Richard Earnshaw", "email": "rearnsha@arm.com", "date": "2021-07-20T10:06:01Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Richard Earnshaw", "email": "rearnsha@arm.com", "date": "2021-07-20T10:14:18Z"}, "message": "Limit fill-column to 79\n\nThe current line-length limit is set to 80, but that allows a\ncharacter to appear in the 80th column, and that causes emacs to\ndisplay a line-wrap followed by a blank line when the display/window\nwidth is 80 columns.  Furthermore, this seems to contradict the\ncoding-style rules on the wiki which suggest that the line limit\nshould be 79.\n\nSo reduce the line width in both the emacs control file and the\ncontrib vimrc file to 79 characters.\n\nChangeLog:\n\n\t* .dir-locals.el (c-mode): Change fill-column to 79.\n\ncontrib/ChangeLog:\n\n\t* vimrc (textwidth): Change non-gitcommit length to 79.", "tree": {"sha": "5393f917d212109c766f7100de16a775a341df9f", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/trees/5393f917d212109c766f7100de16a775a341df9f"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/commits/b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099", "html_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commit/b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099/comments", "author": null, "committer": null, "parents": [{"sha": "b7e450c97340789687b65ab013dbe25e012b0b6c", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/b7e450c97340789687b65ab013dbe25e012b0b6c", "html_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commit/b7e450c97340789687b65ab013dbe25e012b0b6c"}], "stats": {"total": 4, "additions": 2, "deletions": 2}, "files": [{"sha": "b07a0dc50d8a440d5b51ef00953a44de42bfe328", "filename": ".dir-locals.el", "status": "modified", "additions": 1, "deletions": 1, "changes": 2, "blob_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/blob/b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099/.dir-locals.el", "raw_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099/.dir-locals.el", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/.dir-locals.el?ref=b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099", "patch": "@@ -20,4 +20,4 @@\n  (nil . ((bug-reference-url-format . \"http://gcc.gnu.org/PR%s\")))\n  (c-mode . ((c-file-style . \"GNU\")\n \t    (indent-tabs-mode . t)\n-\t    (fill-column . 80))))\n+\t    (fill-column . 79))))"}, {"sha": "b7a8ab7360c377e380948d22a3b313be51b5a083", "filename": "contrib/vimrc", "status": "modified", "additions": 1, "deletions": 1, "changes": 2, "blob_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/blob/b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099/contrib%2Fvimrc", "raw_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099/contrib%2Fvimrc", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/contrib%2Fvimrc?ref=b51de13d81920f92ebe067b9c76e9d2195685099", "patch": "@@ -42,7 +42,7 @@ function! SetStyle()\n   if &filetype == \"gitcommit\"\n     setlocal textwidth=72\n   else\n-    setlocal textwidth=80\n+    setlocal textwidth=79\n   endif\n   setlocal formatoptions-=ro formatoptions+=cqlt\n   if index(l:c_exts, l:ext) != -1 || &filetype == \"c\" || &filetype == \"cpp\""}]}